---++ Sentence Selection

%TOC%

---++++ LexRank: Setup using Dragon Toolkit 
   * [[SentenceSelectionLexRankSimple][Setup for Simple Example]]
   
---++++ Graph based
   * Sentence centrality: LexPageRank
   * Directed Graphs: Hidden Markov Models (HMM)
   * Undirected Graphs: Conditional Random Fields (CRF)

---++++ Query-related (user needs)
   * Maximal Marginal Relevance (MMR)
      * -> Topic selected by the user
      * -> User profile representing information needs (to be trained)
      * -> Individual summary: Selection of Summary-Sentences related to user (needs)

---++++ Others
   * Randomized local search
   * Relevance measure and latent semantic analysis
   * Maximum entropy